{"title_page": "2018 World Long Distance Mountain Running Championships", "text_new": "{{Infobox Athletics Championships\n|Name = 2018 World Long Distance Mountain Running Championships\n|Logo = \n|Size = \n|Optional caption = \n|Host city = [[Karpacz]], [[Poland]]\n|Dates = 24 June\n|Stadium = \n|Nations participating = \n|Athletes participating = \n|Events = 4\n|Records set = \n|Level = Senior\n|Previous = [[2017 World Long Distance Mountain Running Championships|2017]]\n|Next     = [[2019 World Long Distance Mountain Running Championships|2019]]\n}}\nThe '''2018 World Long Distance Mountain Running Challenge''' was the 15th edition of the global [[Mountain running]] competition, [[World Long Distance Mountain Running Championships]], organised by the [[World Mountain Running Association]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wmra.ch/results/world-long-distance-challenge-championships|title=World Long Distance Mountain Running Challenge (2018-2018)/Championships (2015 on)|publisher=wmra.ch|accessdate=11 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Results==\n===Individual===\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n====Men====\n{| class=\"wikitable\" width=80% style=\"font-size:90%; text-align:left;\"\n|-\n!Rank !! Athlete !! Country !! Time\n|-\n|align=\"center\"| {{M\u00e9daille d'or}}\n|[[Alessandro Rambaldini]]\n|{{ITA}}\n|{{Heure|2|39|18}}\n|-\n|align=\"center\"| {{M\u00e9daille d'argent}}\n|[[Robert Krupi\u010dka]]\n|{{CZE}}\n|{{Heure|2|40|55}}\n|-\n|align=\"center\"| {{M\u00e9daille de bronze}}\n|[[Joseph Gray (runner)|Joseph Gray]]\n|{{USA}}\n|{{Heure|2|41|02}}\n|-\n|align=\"center\"| 4\n|[[Ji\u0159\u00ed \u010c\u00edpa]]\n|{{CZE}}\n|{{Heure|2|44|27}}\n|-\n|align=\"center\"| 5\n|[[Andy Wacker]]\n|{{USA}}\n|{{Heure|2|45|21}}\n|-\n|align=\"center\"| 6\n|[[Jonathan Schmid (runner)|Jonathan Schmid]]\n|{{SUI}}\n|{{Heure|2|45|34}}\n|-\n|align=\"center\"| 7\n|[[Ionut Zinca]]\n|{{ROU}}\n|{{Heure|2|46|06}}\n|-\n|align=\"center\"| 8\n|[[Murray Strain]]\n|{{GBR}}\n|{{Heure|2|46|29}}\n|-\n|align=\"center\"| 