ad Bradford|Bradford]] (1\u20131) || '''[[Dan Wheeler|Wheeler]]''' (0\u20131) || [[George Sherrill|Sherrill]] (5) || 19,295 || 5\u20136\n|- style=\"text-align:center; background:#bfb;\"\n| 12 || April 13 || [[Baltimore Orioles|Orioles]] || 6\u20132 || '''[[Jeff Niemann|Niemann]]''' (1\u20130) || [[Brian Burres|Burres]]  (1\u20131) ||  || 16,748 || 6\u20136\n|- style=\"text-align:center; background:#fbb;\"\n| 13 || April 14 || [[New York Yankees|Yankees]] || 8\u20137 || [[Brian Bruney|Bruney]] (1\u20130) || '''[[Al Reyes|Reyes]]''' (1\u20132) || [[Mariano Rivera|Rivera]] (4) || 18,872 || 6\u20137\n|- style=\"text-align:center; background:#fbb;\"\n| 14 || April 15 || [[New York Yankees|Yankees]] || 5\u20133 || [[Andy Pettitte|Pettitte]] (2\u20131) || '''[[Edwin Jackson (baseball)|Jackson]]''' (2\u20131)  || [[Mariano Rivera|Rivera]] (5) || 20,923 || 6\u20138\n|- style=\"text-align:center; background:#fbb;\"\n| 15 || April 16 || @ [[Minnesota Twins|Twins]] || 6\u20135 || [[Juan Rinc\u00f3n|Rinc\u00f3n]] (1\u20130) || '''[[Dan Wheeler|Wheeler]]''' (0\u20132) || [[Joe Nathan|Nathan]] (5) || 20,209 || 6\u20139\n|- style=\"text-align:center; background:#bfb;\"\n| 16 || April 17 || @ [[Minnesota Twins|Twins]] || 7\u20133 || '''[[Jason Hammel (baseball)|Hammel]]''' (1\u20131) || [[Boof Bonser|Bonser]] (1\u20133) || '''[[J.P. Howell|Howell]]''' (1) || 14,781 || 7\u20139\n|- style=\"text-align:center; background:#fbb;\"\n| 17 || April 18 || [[Chicago White Sox|White Sox]] || 9\u20132 || [[Javier V\u00e1zquez (baseball)|V\u00e1zquez]] (3\u20131) || '''[[Jeff Niemann|Niemann]]''' (1\u20131) || || 12,379 || 7\u201310\n|- style=\"text-align:center; background:#bfb;\"\n| 18 || April 19 || [[Chicago White Sox|White Sox]] || 5\u20130 || '''[[Andy Sonnanstine|Sonnanstine]]''' (2\u20131) || [[Mark Buehrle|Buehrle]] (1\u20132) || || 17,613 || 8\u201310\n|- style=\"text-align:center; background:#fbb;\"\n| 19 || April 20 || [[Chicago White Sox|White Sox]] || 6\u20130 || [[John Danks|Danks